38
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:58,570
Tim Akuntansi
Kim Yumi

39
00:04:58,570 --> 00:05:02,620
Dia bekerja sangat keras sehingga dia dipromosikan bulan lalu.

40
00:05:02,620 --> 00:05:04,040
Asisten Manajer Kim.

41
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,990
