83
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,200
Asisten Manajer Kim, kopi Anda ada di sini.

84
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:09,520
Hai Yumi, pekerja kedai kopi itu sangat tampan.

85
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:18,870
